shorter
sections.&nbsp;</li>
<li>
<strong>
Skillfully
use
bold
and/or
italicized
type
to
emphasize
main
points.</strong>&nbsp;Do
so
sparingly.
Overuse
of
bold
or
italicized
type
looks
unprofessional
and
